title: 2BD - Spacious Garden Unit
posting_body: ['Park Shores is a quintessential courtyard walk-up in Chicago’s historic family friendly Buena Park Neighborhood, home to the most beautiful lakeside mansions and Georgian architecture.', 'This large garden unit features full size appliances, central heating, a dishwasher and hardwood flooring.', 'This unit (#4306-0A) is now on special for only $1,550 per month!', 'Community Amenities:', '- Courtyard', '- On-Site Laundry Facility', '- Easy Access to Public Transportation', '- Indoor Bike Storage', 'About the Location:', '- Wrigleyville', '- CTA Access', '- Lake Michigan', '- Montrose', '- Target', 'Visit our website for more information and to view live availability: <URL>', 'Disclaimer: Pricing, availability, lease terms and specials are subject to change.', 'Apartment availability and lease terms may vary.', 'Please note that the price may be net effective of a special and/or concessions that are currently running.', 'Pictures may be of similar unit with similar finishes.', 'Information is believed to be accurate, however, is subject to errors and omissions.', 'Group Fox Management | Equal Housing Opportunity']
